_:Nc281c7a605e4432fac010ce96779ea0b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Sir Nigel was appointed Chair of the Committee on Radioactive Waste Management on 2 July 2018.</p>\n\n<p>Until 2017, Sir Nigel was the Executive Director of Schwarzman Scholars. He is one of the world’s leading human geographers and previously served as Vice-Chancellor and President of the University of Warwick and as Pro-Vice-Chancellor for Research at the University of Oxford.</p>\n\n<p>Term of office ends: January 2028 (extended)</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
